short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View all deals in your personal Amazon Wish List.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
View all the product and best deals in your personal Amazon Wish List.

Load you complete Amazon Wish List and allow to search products, available items and sort by price, current discount and AZwish score. 

This local extension does not collect, transmit or share any information, personal, products, prices or otherwise.

Full source is available at: https://github.com/AZ-Wish/AZ-WishList
